Description: A simple Qt6 text editor
 Mo is a modern text editor built with Qt6 Widgets.
 .
 Features:
  * Multi-tab interface
  * Syntax highlighting (200+ languages via KSyntaxHighlighting)
  * Automatic encoding detection (libuchardet)
  * Session restore
  * Find and replace
  * Wayland native
